name: Adventure Map Algonquin - Canoe Lake Map
description: This Algonquin Park map covers the area from Ragged Lake in the south to Baby Joe Lake in the north, and from Tea Lake in the west to Source and Tanamakoon lakes in the east. It includes the popular Canoe Lake and Smoke Lake access points, plus the Tom Thomson Lake area. The back of the map features information on local history, hiking trails, park facilities, and trip tips.
